copy:
.config/50-synaptics /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/50-synaptics
.config/20-intel -> ditto

when updating linux or linux-headers (kernel), do the following:
    rebuild broadcom-wl
    move new kernel files to /dev/sda2/
